{
  "stem": "15686.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were about two days out of Lisbon when the boat came to a stop one morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was very unusual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we ran up, got dressed, and run-- ran up on the deck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there was a German submarine that had stopped us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And although we were neutral, they had said, 'well, you're neutral--' we found this out later when the crew explained it-- 'you have enemies of the Third Reich on board, and we have to control your passenger list.' And they directed us to go to the nearest port, which happened to be Casablanca in Morocco.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And Casablanca, Morocco, was under the Vichy government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was still a French colony, and it was under the Vichy government rules.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The political situation at that point in France was very confusing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You had the Vichy government, you had the free French under the Gaulle operating out of London, and in North Africa, you had another free French group, which was, however, collaborating with Vichy under a general called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were all fighting each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in Morocco, some Germans and Vichy French gendarmes came on board, and they wanted to see our papers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all I had was a French residence permit, which I had received when I got to Chabannes, and I had to go to the police there every month to have it stamped so I could stay another month.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I showed them that, and they wanted to know, did I have any photographs that would show any buildings, or bridges, or, you know, things of that sort.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said no, I have no photographs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't have anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
